---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";

import kalachakraIcon from "../assets/icons/kalachakra-icon.webp";
import kalachakraMantra from "../assets/icons/kalachakra-mantra.svg";
---

<footer class="flex flex-col items-center gap-10 bg-gray-200 p-6 px-4 pb-4">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row">
      <Image class="mx-auto" src={kalachakraIcon} alt="" width="125" />
      <Image class="mx-auto" src={kalachakraMantra} alt="" height="150" />
    </div>
    <div class="mt-2 max-w-[345px] text-center text-xs italic">
      <div class="text-sx mb-2 font-bold not-italic">
        Om Ha Ksha Ma La Va Ra Yang Svaha
      </div>
       May the sacred Kalachakra mantra bring wisdom, compassion, and
      enlightenment to all beings.
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 md:flex-row md:gap-16">
    <div class="">
      <div class="leading-tight">
        Jonang Takten Phuntsok Choeling<br /> Tibetan Buddhist Monastery,<br />
         Sanjauli 171006, Shimla,<br />
         Himachal Pradesh, INDIA
      </div>
      <div class="mt-2 leading-tight">
        EMAIL: office@jonangmonastery.com<br /> PHONE: +91 177 2841410
      </div>
    </div>
    <button class="text-bold h-10 w-32 rounded bg-yellow-500 text-lg"
      >Donate</button
